					<div class="item" style="background-image: url('/images/rooms/star_06.jpg')"></div>
					<div class="item" style="background-image: url('/images/rooms/star_07.jpg')"></div>
					<div class="item" style="background-image: url('/images/rooms/star_08.jpg')"></div>
					<button class="slidesjs-previous slidesjs-navigation btn-default">&lt;</button>
					<button class="slidesjs-next slidesjs-navigation btn-default">&gt;</button>
				</div>
				<div class="facilities">
					<p class="title">구비시설</p>
					<p>TV, 에어컨, 온풍기, 냉장고, 전기밥솥, 커피포트, 인덕션, 전기쿠커, 냄비 등 조리기구, 헤어드라이어, 침대, 샤워부스, 수건,
